<pb facs="1079261" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Pereximio at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">U+E8BF</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Celeberrimo Viro
             <lb/>Petro Antonio <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelotti</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><choice><abbr>Joh.</abbr><expan>Johannes</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>.</salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Poteram in postremis meis <rs key="B_1721-07-30_991170515149905501" type="letter">litteris</rs><note type="editorial">Meint den letzten Brief Johann I Bernoullis vom 30. Juli 1721</note> omittere argumentum
         <lb/>illud quod inter alia ex abundanti adjeci ad infringendam demon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>strationem <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatianam</rs>, reliqua suffecissent; Hoc quippe, in
         <lb/>quo Tibi jam scrupulus superest et quod est ex eorum
         <lb/>numero, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vocantur <hi rendition="#u">argumenta ad hominem</hi> non habebat
         <lb/>alium finem, quam ut ostenderem, ex modo ratiocinandi
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtoniano</rs> et <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatiano</rs> deduci posse, <hi rendition="#u">vim qu<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> totus aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
            <lb/>exilientis motus generari possit, <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualem esse ponderi cylin<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>dric<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, cujus basis est foramen <formula>EF</formula> (<choice><abbr>vid.</abbr><expan>vide</expan></choice>
<lb/><choice><abbr>fig.</abbr><expan>figuram</expan></choice> pag. 306<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> <choice><orig>princ.</orig><reg><abbr>Princ.</abbr><expan>Principorum</expan></reg></choice> <choice><abbr>Phil.</abbr><expan>Philosophiae</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Edit.</abbr><expan>Editionis</expan></choice> 2<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>) et altitudo non tantum
            <lb/><formula>2GI</formula> vel <formula>2CK</formula> sed qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>libet alia, id est, vim invariatam
            <lb/>et constantem fore <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualem ponderi indeterminato et cuicun<choice><orig><g ref="#que">U+E8BF</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice></hi>;
         <lb/>quod uti<choice><orig><g ref="#que">U+E8BF</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> valde absurdum; quod vero instanti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> loco ad argumen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tum <add>illud</add> meum reponis ex eo tantum venit, quod me non recte
         <lb/>intellexisti, putas enim me aliam supponere velocitatem
         <lb/>aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> effluentis, quam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> supponitur <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtono</rs> et
         <pb facs="1079262" n="2"/>
<rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccato</rs> et qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ab illis repr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentatur per <formula>2GI</formula>; Verum enimvero
         <lb/>id quod mere arbitrarium est assumo diversum ab eo,
         <lb/>quod illi Viri assumserunt, nempe tempus per quod
         <lb/>durat aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> effluxus; illi assumserunt tempus <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quale ei,
         <lb/>quod insumeret aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> gutta cadens per simplicem alti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tudinem <formula>IG</formula>, sed ego eodem jure assumsi tempus per
         <lb/>quod durat aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> effluxus (durare enim potest quamdiu
         <lb/>lubet) <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quale ei quod impenderet aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> gutta cadens
         <lb/>per quamlibet aliam altitudinem ex. gr. per <formula>4GI</formula>, quod
         <lb/>tempus cum sit duplo majus quam quod <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtono</rs>
<lb/>et <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccato</rs> assumitur, erit certe etiam quantitas aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/>eo tempore effluentis duplo major quam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tempore simplo
         <lb/>effluit, <choice><abbr>h.</abbr><expan>hoc</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>e.</abbr><expan>est</expan></choice> erit <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quale cylindro aqueo, cujus basis est
         <lb/>foramen <formula>EF</formula> et altitudo <formula>4GI</formula>: Vides itaque, Vir <choice><abbr>Cl.</abbr><expan>Clarissime</expan></choice>,
         <lb/>me retenta cum <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccato</rs> et <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtono</rs> velocitate express<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> per
         <lb/><formula>2GI</formula> posse eodem modo ac illi fecerunt concludere
         <lb/>vim, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> totus aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> exilientis motus generari potest
         <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualem esse ponderi cylindric<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/>cujus basis est foramen <formula>EF</formula> et altitudo <formula>4GI</formula>.<note type="editorial">Hier muss noch geklärt werden, ob dieser Punkt stehen bleibt bzw. ob "regerent" gross geschrieben werden soll.</note> regerent
         <lb/>meum tempus esse duplo majus suo tempore, respondebo
         <lb/>ipsorum tempus esse dupl<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> minus meo tempore:
         <pb facs="1079263" n="3"/>
<lb/>instabunt suum tempus esse id, quod supponi debet,
         <lb/>ego vero reponam, meum tempus eodem jure supponi
         <lb/>posse, nihil enim in rei natur<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> video quod unum
         <lb/>potius quam alterum exigat, sin quid illi vident,
         <lb/>monstrent doceant<choice><orig><g ref="#que">U+E8BF</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> cur effluxus duratio non possit pro
         <lb/>lubitu supponi: profecto qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> acrius rem istam expendo,
         <lb/>e<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> ineptius mihi videtur assertum <rs key="biblio_6CP8LL78" type="biblio"><choice><abbr>Coroll.</abbr><expan>Corollarii</expan></choice></rs><note type="editorial">werktag: newtonbhbd für die 1713er-Ausgabe der Principia schon eingesetzt: Newton, Isaac, Philosophiae naturalis principia mathematica. Editio secunda auctior et emendatior, Cantabrigiae [Cambridge] (C. Crownfield) 1713. Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Johann I Bernoulli und Johann Jakob Scheuchzer.</note> 2. <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person"><choice><abbr>Newton.</abbr><expan>Newtoniani</expan></choice></rs> p. 307<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice><supplied>,</supplied>
<lb/>duas enim absurditates simul ibi committit. 1<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice><hi rendition="#sup">o</hi> comparat
         <lb/>vim acceleratricem cum pondere, hoc est, comparat duas
         <lb/>quantitates heterogeneas; 2<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice><hi rendition="#sup">o</hi> vim suam acceleratricem
         <lb/>suo ratiocinandi modo cuicun<choice><orig><g ref="#que">U+E8BF</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> alii ponderi <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualem
         <lb/>facere posset, hoc est, determinatum <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quale facit indeter<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>minato. Sed h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c sufficiant; lege h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so cum attenti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>one, ne ob solam inadvertentiam Tuam cogar oleum et operam inutiliter perdere.</p>
<p><lb/>Legi utramque pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>fationem Tuam, tam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> operi
         <lb/>Tuo quam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Dissertationibus meis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>fixa est,
         <lb/>placent ill<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi, sed multis non perinde placebunt;
         <lb/>Nescio an non ex Thrasonibus Anglis aliquos contra
         <lb/>Te suscitaturus sis; Certe si omnes silerent, unus ille
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-124275087" type="person"><choice><abbr>Joh.</abbr><expan>Johannes</expan></choice> Keillius</rs> homo vanus et turbulentus non silebit;
         <pb facs="1079264" n="4"/>
<lb/>videtur ille rixis et litibus saginari potius quam delectari. Se<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>cundum id quod intellexi ex <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">Litteris</rs><note type="editorial">Im Briefinventar findet sich nur der Brief 000056822 von Nic. II B. an Joh. I B. vom 5. Juni 1716.</note> Filii mei <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Nicolai</rs>
<lb/>novissimis oportet ut cum <choice><abbr>Illustr.</abbr><expan>Illustrissimo</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Excell.</abbr><expan>Excellentissimo</expan></choice> Comite
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-121710742" type="person">Vezzi</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetias</rs> redierit ex acidulis, sed simul audio, ob
         <lb/>perpetuam <choice><abbr>Exc.</abbr><expan>Excellentissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-121710742" type="person">Comitis</rs> valetudinem adversam <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">filium</rs>
<lb/>meum brevi et forte adhuc ante hyemem <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> disces<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>surum atque ad nos remigraturum esse, ideoque si quid ad
         <lb/>me mittendum habes, poteris id ei tradere. Quod superest
         <lb/>mittam ad Te <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filii</rs> mei Dissertationem nunc editam
         <lb/><rs key="biblio_KGZSMV2E" type="biblio">de Respiratione</rs><note type="editorial">Bernoulli, Daniel, Dissertatio Inauguralis Physico-Medica De Respiratione, Quam Consensu <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> Auctoritate Gratiosissimi Medicorum Ordinis in Universitate Patria Pro Summis in Arte Medica Honoribus <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> Privilegiis Doctoralibus rite consequendis, Ad diem 2. Septembr. MDCCXXI L.H.Q.S. Publico Examini subjicit Daniel Bernoulli, Joh. Fil. Basil., [Basel] (J. L. Brandmüller) 1721 (= St. 1). Aus: Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Johann I Bernoulli und Johann Jakob Scheuchzer. Auch in: Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Johann I Bernoulli und Johannes Scheuchzer.</note>, statim ac occasio mittendi sese mihi
         <lb/>obtulerit; spero materiam ibi tractatam Tibi non omnino
         <lb/>displicituram;</p> <closer><salute>Interim vale.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1721-09-06">6<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> <choice><abbr>7bris</abbr><expan>Septembris</expan></choice> 1721.</date></dateline></closer>
</div></body></text></TEI>